The paper discusses encryption schemes and their implementation, which falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). It also involves information theory (cs.IT) as it deals with the privacy concerns of sharing sensitive data. The paper also discusses the practicality of the encryption schemes, which falls under the category of computer science and computational complexity (cs.CC). The implementation of the encryption schemes involves algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and software engineering (cs.SE).
